      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey just had a question about my warfarin. i've been on 5mg for a while now and i honestly feel great. like super healthy and nothing is wrong. i was thinking of dropping down to like 2mg just to see if i can maintain it with a lower dose since i'm doing so well. is that a safe move to try?",
